task.summary: Started with sinks again; nixing for streams; makes an important point about directionality of message flow. Will necessitate writing an asynchronous response handler
Traffic is wired from SendMessageStream->Kad; need to wire a handler for Kad messages to a MessageDispatch and write a provider for it
Incoming traffic wired through MessageHandler composed over MessageDispatch. KadChannel module wires up outgoing and incoming with singleton KeybasedRouting and singleton MessageDispatch
ActivatorProvider is wired to respond to GetResourceMessage. Need to decide on the outermost interface for the channel; probably just by exposing ResourceFinder
Killing new filtering; it's not better.
